      <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:clock-outline" class="w-6 sm:w-7 h-6 sm:h-7 text-cyan-400" />
        Режим работы
